---
import Bi from '../shared/Bi.astro';
import Callout from '../shared/Callout.astro';
import Section from '../mechanics/Section.astro';
---
<Section id="hero-farming" titleZh="第 2 階段：英雄打綠洲" titleEn="Phase 2: Hero oasis farming" eyebrow="Lumi §1">
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="保護期內，野生動物在綠洲上是「一次性獎金」—— 清完不會再生。每隻動物給 160 / 240 / 320 / 480 / 800 資源（依強度）。把英雄全部技能點丟戰鬥力，能在 Day 1–3 內賺 2,000+ 資源，這比把點數塞進「資源採集」前期划算多了。"
      en="During beginner protection, oasis animals are a one-time bounty — once cleared, they don't respawn. Each animal yields 160 / 240 / 320 / 480 / 800 resources by tier. Putting every skill point into Fighting Strength on Day 1–3 nets 2,000+ resources — far more than what Resource Production gives in the same window."
    />
  </p>

  <h3><Bi zh="第 1 次冒險拿馬" en="First adventure → horse" /></h3>
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="不論部族，第一次冒險的獎勵幾乎都會給馬，把英雄速度從 7 拉到 14 格/小時。打更多綠洲、跑更遠、更安全。"
      en="The first adventure almost always rewards a horse, doubling hero speed from 7 to 14 fields/hr. More oases reachable, longer routes, safer escapes."
    />
  </p>

  <Callout kind="tip" titleZh="Strength 分配規則（依可打綠洲數）" titleEn="Strength allocation rule (by accessible oases)">
    <ul>
      <li>
        <Bi
          zh="0 塊綠洲 → 最多加 2 點 strength（太少可打的，投 strength 低 ROI）"
          en="0 oases → max 2 strength points (too little to farm, low ROI on strength)"
        />
      </li>
      <li>
        <Bi
          zh="1-5 塊綠洲 → 加 8-12 點 strength（適度 farming 窗口）"
          en="1-5 oases → 8-12 strength points (moderate farming window)"
        />
      </li>
      <li>
        <Bi
          zh="6 塊以上綠洲 → 加 12+ 點 strength（重 farming，strength 回報好）"
          en="6+ oases → 12+ strength points (heavy farming, strength scales well)"
        />
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <Bi
        zh="原則：英雄不太可能連續 24 小時都有綠洲能打。綠洲打完之後，多餘的 strength 點是浪費；改投資源產量，英雄空閒時也在幫你賺資源。"
        en="Principle: your hero rarely has 24h+ of oasis-clearing activity. Once oases run dry, extra strength points are wasted; invest in resource production instead — hero keeps earning even when idle."
      />
    </p>
  </Callout>

  <h3><Bi zh="保護期結束後 → 切換為資源採集" en="After protection → switch to Resource Production" /></h3>
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="第 3–4 天保護期一結束，英雄打綠洲就可能被反偵察 → 反殺。把屬性透過冒險獲得的「智慧之書」重置，全灌資源採集。"
      en="When protection ends around Day 3–4, oasis raids become suicide runs (other players will counter-attack). Use a Book of Wisdom (from adventures) to respec the hero entirely into Resource Production."
    />
  </p>

  <Callout kind="warn" titleZh="不要讓英雄死掉" titleEn="Don't let your hero die">
    <p>
      <Bi
        zh="英雄死亡 = 24 小時復活 + 失去經驗值。打綠洲前必模擬戰鬥（rally point → 戰鬥模擬器）。早期可帶幾隻便宜兵當肉盾（埃及奴隸民兵特別便宜）。"
        en="A dead hero = 24h respawn + lost XP. Always simulate before clearing an oasis (rally point → battle simulator). Bring cheap troops as buffer (Egyptian Slave Militia are dirt-cheap and ideal for this)."
      />
    </p>
  </Callout>
</Section>
